# Bot deploy — kote (SA + TZ)

**Chanzo cha code (master):** `TipTap_tz_bot/` (sync kutoka `TAPTAP_sauth/tiptopbot/src` ikiwa unahariri huko).

## Bot VPS 2 — lazima zote

| MCP | IP | Path |
|-----|-----|------|
| **TIPTAPsouth bot** | 167.71.44.10 | `/opt/tiptap-sauth-bot/tiptopbot` |
| **TITAPtz bot** | 178.62.61.85 | `/opt/titap-bot/tiptopbot` |

**Usi-deploy bot kwenye Laravel VPS** (`TIPTAP SOUTH AFRICA`, `TIPTAP TZ`).

## Workflow (kila update ya bot)

1. Hariri `src/*.js` kwenye **TipTap_tz_bot** (au sync kutoka `TAPTAP_sauth/tiptopbot/src`).
2. Thibitisha `.env.example`: `USE_INTERACTIVE_MENU=true` (buttons, si menu ya namba).
3. Deploy **zote mbili**:
   ```bash
   cd TipTap_tz_bot && bash scripts/deploy-bot-all.sh
   ```
4. Test: `Hi` / `0` — buttons 3 (Menu, Pay Bill, More), si “Reply with the number”.

## Usifanye

- Update TZ bot pekee na kuacha SA (au kinyume).
- `USE_INTERACTIVE_MENU=false` isipokuwa user ameomba text menu kwa makusudi.
- Deploy bot code kwenye `164.92.242.245` au `139.59.151.111` (Laravel web).

## Laravel (tofauti na bot)

Webhook / `bot_sessions` / `.env` `WHATSAPP_BOT_NOTIFY_URL` — deploy kwenye **Laravel VPS** ya nchi husika, si script hii.
